{"tid":2193064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"余德寶： 昨日被便衣警強行拖走的青年被拒保釋","createTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:39:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8996a4616abd51f1d8ce9f84e6ed8e2b18f8ba0e","tid":2193064,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8tV9c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8tV9c1.jpg&h=13beb5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發！！被便衣警拖走的年輕人被拒保釋<br />\n<br />\n昨日在優才書院被捕的兩名男子暫時被拒保釋，其中一位是被便衣警拖走的年輕人。<br />\n警方正考慮進行檢控，我和律師正協助相關被捕家人。<br />\n<br />\n其餘158位被捕人士已經保釋離開￼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/616177075066304/posts/4028338933850084/?extid=D8ZHogRi3Smmm2Wa&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F616177075066304%2Fposts%2F4028338933850084%2F%3Fextid%3DD8ZHogRi3Smmm2Wa%26d%3Dn&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=8b54c2d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/616177075066304/posts/4028338933850084/?extid=D8ZHogRi3Smmm2Wa&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"449127aefdc73ec6644bee3a2ab3b2fa453b6d27","tid":2193064,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd1bfd2be7e4974045bfcffb8e3ccd4d444e6c3","tid":2193064,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c31318301f54dd1ed2c314ab5f5da9015fceff5","tid":2193064,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\"